# mrx-link-core

> `mrx-link-core` is a package that contains the core functions related to pipeline operation for `mrx-link`. `mrx-link-core` is automatically installed when `mrx-link` is installed. Please refer to the following link if you wish to use the `mrx-link` package.

* Visit [mrx-link](https://pypi.org/project/mrx-link/)

## Usage Environment

| Supported Platform | Linux (AMD64, ARM64) / macOS (Intel, Apple Silicon) / Windows |
| ------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Python Version     | `3.7`, `3.8`, `3.9`, `3.10`                                   |
